00:09:00.090 --> 00:09:01.500
And I should mention,
remember how the motors

00:09:01.500 --> 00:09:04.650
from the fake video could
barely lift only six quarters?

00:09:04.650 --> 00:09:07.410
Well, if you properly size
them for the task at hand,

00:09:07.410 --> 00:09:10.260
they should be able to lift 150 quarters.

00:09:10.260 --> 00:09:12.510
And so once we felt like we
had it in pretty good shape,

00:09:12.510 --> 00:09:15.275
we took her out for
the maiden test flight.

00:09:15.275 --> 00:09:17.858
