00:09:41.040 --> 00:09:43.470
The reason pretty much all
camera drones are quad-copter

00:09:43.470 --> 00:09:44.880
is because they're much more stable due

00:09:44.880 --> 00:09:47.790
to a larger footprint
shared between four motors.

00:09:47.790 --> 00:09:49.860
And by getting clever
with a throttle speeds,

00:09:49.860 --> 00:09:51.660
you can move in all six degrees of freedom

00:09:51.660 --> 00:09:53.010
with no moving parts.

00:09:53.010 --> 00:09:54.570
So there you go, with solid engineering,

00:09:54.570 --> 00:09:57.390
you don't need hidden rods
or masking and rotoscoping,

00:09:57.390 --> 00:09:58.620
and Sir Isaac Newton

00:09:58.620 --> 00:10:01.680
can once again comfortably
rest in his grave.

00:10:01.680 --> 00:10:02.640
So the moral of the story

00:10:02.640 --> 00:10:05.160
is just don't cheat and lie and scam.

